markdownRemark.html: In an important new article, Robert Black has analyzed the amount of material Aldo Manuzio took over from earlier grammarians for his highly respected introductory Latin grammar: "Aldo Manuzio Grammarian," in Collectanea manuziana. Studi critici su Aldo Manuzio, ed. by P.D. Accendere and S.U. Baldassari (Florence: Le Lettere, 2017), pp. 65-92.
